    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, so it\u2019s super clean and runs like a charm. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this beauty for yourself! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
