      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional multi-stage polish and ceramic coating, with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather is soft and free of any creasing, the original floor mats are pristine, and the 'new car' scent persists. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, with full documentation included. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor, offering a tight, responsive, and rattle-free experience.",
